  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Alex Antoniou</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"la\">  <span class=\"textpartnumber\" id=\"aba\">fragment (physical) a</span>  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"diva--interpretive\">  <a id=\"aa-l1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<span data-text=\"dius\">dius</span>  <span data-text=\"prim\">prim</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] </span></div>  <span class=\"textpartnumber\" id=\"abb\">fragment (physical) b</span>  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"divb--interpretive\">  <a id=\"ab-l1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]triarchus </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Alex Antoniou</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"la\"><span class=\"textpartnumber\" id=\"aba\">fragment (physical) a</span><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"diva--diplomatic\"><a id=\"aa-l1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<span data-text=\"dius\">DIUS</span><span data-text=\"prim\">PRIM</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]</span></div><span class=\"textpartnumber\" id=\"abb\">fragment (physical) b</span><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"divb--diplomatic\"><a id=\"ab-l1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]TRIARCHUS</span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span><span>Text of Gualtherus</span></span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2> translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\">  </p><p>  </p></div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>Gualtherus observes that the two fragments were set close to each other and should originally have been connected.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li></li><li> Gualtherus 1624 34 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002388\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002388</a>  </li><li> Gualtherus 1624 [1625] 191 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001931\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001931</a>  </li><li> Mommsen 1883 <a href=\"http://arachne.uni-koeln.de/books/CILv10pII1883\" target=\"_blank\">7291</a>  <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000589\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000589</a></li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> Line 1    Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence.  </div>",
